{
  "title": "卡尔 vs 威尔逊",
  "subtitle": "两个青少年，两种 AI 哲学",
  "date": "",
  "badge": "致远见卓识的 CTO",
  "originally_published": "<p style=\"margin:0\"><strong>最初发表于 <a href=\"https://pragmatismo.com.br/blog/carl-vs-wilson/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">pragmatismo.com.br</a></strong></p>",
  "body": "<section class=\"section\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"card-grid card-grid-2\">\n<div class=\"card\">\n<div class=\"card-header-center\">\n<div class=\"avatar-circle avatar-blue\">\n<svg width=\"32\" height=\"32\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"white\" stroke-width=\"2\"><rect x=\"3\" y=\"11\" width=\"18\" height=\"11\" rx=\"2\" ry=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4\"></path></svg>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"text-blue\">卡尔，17岁</h3>\n<p>崇拜大厂营销</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"card-body\">\n<div class=\"callout callout-blue\">\n<h4>卡尔的画像：</h4>\n<p>卡尔代表了传统的企业思维：“如果它对每个人都管用，那么对我也管用。”他真诚地认为，沿着数万人已经铺平的道路前行是最聪明的策略。毕竟，当微软（超级英雄）已经做好了这一切工作时，为什么要重新发明轮子呢？</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>从 ChatGPT 复制的提示词</strong> — “如果能抄，为什么要自己写？”</li>\n<li><strong>官方文档就是法律</strong> — 只有带有微软 Logo 的文档才信得过</li>\n<li><strong>5分钟极速安装</strong> — 为自己不动脑筋而自豪</li>\n<li><strong>把 Stack Overflow 奉为圣经</strong> — 社区里总能找到答案</li>\n<li><strong>自动更新</strong> — 让大厂替他做决定</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"callout-note\">卡尔没有意识到他正在构建与竞争对手完全相同的产品……</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"badge-row\">\n<span class=\"badge badge-blue\">可靠 <svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#22c55e\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"display:inline;vertical-align:middle;margin-right:2px\"><polyline points=\"20 6 9 17 4 12\"/></svg></span>\n<span class=\"badge badge-emerald\">快速上手 <svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#f59e0b\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"display:inline;vertical-align:middle\"><polygon points=\"13 2 3 14 12 14 11 22 21 10 12 10 13 2\"/></svg></span>\n<span class=\"badge badge-gray\">同质化商品 <svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"display:inline;vertical-align:middle\"><path d=\"M16.5 9.4 7.55 4.24\"/><path d=\"M21 16V8a2 2 0 0 0-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 0 0 3 8v8a2 2 0 0 0 1 1.73l7 4a2 2 0 0 0 2 0l7-4A2 2 0 0 0 21 16z\"/><polyline points=\"3.29 7 12 12 20.71 7\"/><line x1=\"12\" y1=\"22\" x2=\"12\" y2=\"12\"/></svg></span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"card\">\n<div class=\"card-header-center\">\n<div class=\"avatar-circle avatar-purple\">\n<svg width=\"32\" height=\"32\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"white\" stroke-width=\"2\"><rect x=\"3\" y=\"11\" width=\"18\" height=\"11\" rx=\"2\" ry=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 9.9-1\"></path></svg>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"text-purple\">威尔逊，17岁</h3>\n<p>独立创新者</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"card-body\">\n<div class=\"callout callout-purple\">\n<h4>威尔逊的画像：</h4>\n<p>威尔逊在不彻底弄清内部原理之前是不会使用某样东西的。他将每个问题都视为创造全新事物的机会，即使这意味着要花费更多的时间。</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>多样化的本地 LLM</strong> — “我的数据，我的规则”</li>\n<li><strong>无人想到的提示词</strong> — 尝试颠覆性的方法</li>\n<li><strong>完全原创的代码</strong> — 旨在减少地球资源消耗的技术栈</li>\n<li><strong>定制化基础设施</strong> — 每个决策都是深思熟虑的</li>\n<li><strong>量身定制的算法</strong> — 真正的竞争优势</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"callout-note callout-note-green\">威尔逊正在构建 3-5 年后将成为行业标准的产品……</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"badge-row\">\n<span class=\"badge badge-purple\">创造力</span>\n<span class=\"badge badge-pink\">可定制</span>\n<span class=\"badge badge-cyan\">创新性</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n\n<section class=\"section\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<h2 class=\"text-center\">两种哲学，两种结果</h2>\n<div class=\"prose max-width\">\n<p>卡尔和威尔逊之间的区别不仅在于他们选择的工具，还在于他们解决问题时的思维模式。每种方法都有其优势，并代表了截然不同的业务战略。</p>\n<p>卡尔代表了重视稳定性、可预测性和快速实施的企业。他的方法非常适合需要一致结果且流程完善的组织。</p>\n<p>威尔逊代表了通过技术创新寻求竞争差异化的企业。他的方法是那些希望创建独特解决方案并对技术栈拥有完全控制权的组织的理想选择。</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"card-grid card-grid-2\" style=\"margin-top:2rem;\">\n<div class=\"card card-blue-tint\">\n<h3 class=\"text-blue\" style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.5rem;\">\n<svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path d=\"M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z\"></path><polyline points=\"9 22 9 12 15 12 15 22\"></polyline></svg>\n大厂世界：舒适区\n</h3>\n<div class=\"callout-quote\">\"既然大厂已经帮你动过脑筋了，为什么还要自己思考？\"</div>\n<div class=\"feature-item\">\n<div>\n<h4>羊群安全感</h4>\n<p>ISO、SOC2、GDPR 认证……在纸面上看都非常引人注目。但当每个人都使用同一种解决方案时，<strong>黑客也知道该往哪里攻击</strong>。这就像全镇的每家每户都使用同一种锁一样。</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature-item\">\n<div>\n<h4>可预测性……还是陷阱？</h4>\n<p>刚开始很便宜对吧？但当你的公司壮大并产生依赖时，<strong>价格就会神奇地上涨</strong>。然后你就会发现，迁移技术栈的花费比付高昂的订阅费还要多。</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature-item\">\n<div>\n<h4>克隆社区</h4>\n<p>详尽的文档？太棒了！数百万开发者都在做同样的事？<strong>你的公司成了芸芸众生中平庸的一员</strong>。零差异化，零竞争优势。</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"callout-warning\">现实：你不是在购买技术，你是在租用依赖。</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"card card-purple-tint\">\n<h3 class=\"text-purple\" style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.5rem;\">\n<svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><polyline points=\"16 18 22 12 16 6\"></polyline><polyline points=\"8 6 2 12 8 18\"></polyline></svg>\n开源路径\n</h3>\n<div class=\"feature-item\">\n<div>\n<h4>差异化创新</h4>\n<p>能够创造出市场上不存在的、真正独特的解决方案。使开发特定的功能成为可持续且难以复制的竞争优势。</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature-item\">\n<div>\n<h4>完全自主</h4>\n<p>对数据、算法和基础设施的完全控制。在关键功能上不依赖第三方，并能根据需要修改系统的任何方面。</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature-item\">\n<div>\n<h4>个性化扩展性</h4>\n<p>针对企业特定需求优化的架构，从而实现更好的性能和优化的成本。能够仅扩展必要的组件。</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n\n<section class=\"section section-alt\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<h2 class=\"text-center\">详细技术对比</h2>\n<div class=\"table-responsive\">\n<table class=\"comparison-table\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>维度</th>\n<th class=\"text-blue\">卡尔 (OpenAI)</th>\n<th class=\"text-purple\">威尔逊 (开源)</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr><td>实施时间</td><td class=\"text-center\"><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#f59e0b\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"display:inline;vertical-align:middle\"><polygon points=\"13 2 3 14 12 14 11 22 21 10 12 10 13 2\"/></svg> 1-2 周</td><td class=\"text-center\"><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#64748b\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"display:inline;vertical-align:middle\"><path d=\"M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 0 0 1.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 0 1-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 0 1-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 0 1 7.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z\"/></svg> 2-3 个月</td></tr>\n<tr><td>初始成本</td><td class=\"text-center\"><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#22c55e\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"display:inline;vertical-align:middle\"><rect x=\"2\" y=\"6\" width=\"20\" height=\"12\" rx=\"2\"/><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"2\"/><path d=\"M6 12h.01M18 12h.01\"/></svg> 中等</td><td class=\"text-center\"><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#22c55e\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"display:inline;vertical-align:middle\"><path d=\"M21 12a9 9 0 0 1-9 9H3l3-3a8 8 0 1 1 15-6z\"/><path d=\"M3 12h6\"/><path d=\"M9 12V8\"/></svg> 低</td></tr>\n<tr><td>自定义程度</td><td class=\"text-center text-red\"><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#ef4444\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"display:inline;vertical-align:middle\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"/><line x1=\"15\" y1=\"9\" x2=\"9\" y2=\"15\"/><line x1=\"9\" y1=\"9\" x2=\"15\" y2=\"15\"/></svg> 受限</td><td class=\"text-center text-green\"><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#22c55e\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"display:inline;vertical-align:middle;margin-right:2px\"><path d=\"M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14\"/><polyline points=\"22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01\"/></svg> 完全</td></tr>\n<tr><td>数据控制权</td><td class=\"text-center text-yellow\"><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#f59e0b\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"display:inline;vertical-align:middle\"><path d=\"M10.29 3.86L1.82 18a2 2 0 0 0 1.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 0 0 1.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 0 0-3.42 0z\"/><line x1=\"12\" y1=\"9\" x2=\"12\" y2=\"13\"/><line x1=\"12\" y1=\"17\" x2=\"12.01\" y2=\"17\"/></svg> 部分</td><td class=\"text-center text-green\"><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#22c55e\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"display:inline;vertical-align:middle;margin-right:2px\"><path d=\"M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14\"/><polyline points=\"22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01\"/></svg> 完全</td></tr>\n<tr><td>可扩展性</td><td class=\"text-center text-green\"><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#888888\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"display:inline;vertical-align:middle\"><polyline points=\"23 6 13.5 15.5 8.5 10.5 1 18\"/><polyline points=\"17 6 23 6 23 12\"/></svg> 高</td><td class=\"text-center text-green\"><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#888888\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"display:inline;vertical-align:middle\"><polyline points=\"23 6 13.5 15.5 8.5 10.5 1 18\"/><polyline points=\"17 6 23 6 23 12\"/></svg> 无限制</td></tr>\n<tr><td>创新性</td><td class=\"text-center text-yellow\"><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#888888\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"display:inline;vertical-align:middle\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"/><line x1=\"2\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"22\" y2=\"12\"/><path d=\"M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4-10z\"/></svg> 渐进式</td><td class=\"text-center text-purple\"><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#888888\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"display:inline;vertical-align:middle\"><path d=\"M4.5 16.5c-1.5 1.26-2 5-2 5s3.74-.5 5-2c.71-.84.7-2.13-.09-2.91a2.18 2.18 0 0 0-2.91-.09z\"/><path d=\"M12 15l-3-3a22 22 0 0 1 2-3.95A12.88 12.88 0 0 1 22 2c0 2.72-.78 7.5-6 11a22.35 22.35 0 0 1-4 2z\"/><path d=\"M9 12H4s.55-3.03 2-4c1.62-1.08 5 0 5 0\"/><path d=\"M12 15v5s3.03-.55 4-2c1.08-1.62 0-5 0-5\"/></svg> 颠覆性</td></tr>\n<tr><td>竞争优势</td><td class=\"text-center text-red\"><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#ef4444\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"display:inline;vertical-align:middle\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"/><line x1=\"15\" y1=\"9\" x2=\"9\" y2=\"15\"/><line x1=\"9\" y1=\"9\" x2=\"15\" y2=\"15\"/></svg> 同质化</td><td class=\"text-center text-green\"><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#22c55e\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"display:inline;vertical-align:middle;margin-right:2px\"><path d=\"M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14\"/><polyline points=\"22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01\"/></svg> 独特</td></tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n\n<section class=\"section\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<h2 class=\"text-center\">CTO 决策框架</h2>\n<div class=\"card-grid card-grid-3\">\n<div class=\"card text-center\">\n<div class=\"avatar-circle avatar-orange\" style=\"margin:0 auto 1rem;\">\n<svg width=\"32\" height=\"32\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"white\" stroke-width=\"2\"><polygon points=\"13 2 3 14 12 14 11 22 21 10 12 10 13 2\"></polygon></svg>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"text-orange\">紧迫性</h3>\n<p>CEO 观念陈旧，深信大厂？卡尔是你的选择。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"card text-center\">\n<div class=\"avatar-circle avatar-purple\" style=\"margin:0 auto 1rem;\">\n<svg width=\"32\" height=\"32\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"white\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path d=\"M12 2a8 8 0 0 0-8 8c0 3.4 2.1 6.3 5 7.5V20h6v-2.5c2.9-1.2 5-4.1 5-7.5a8 8 0 0 0-8-8z\"></path></svg>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"text-purple\">战略</h3>\n<p>渴望面向未来的自由？威尔逊提供独特的竞争优势。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"card text-center\">\n<div class=\"avatar-circle avatar-teal\" style=\"margin:0 auto 1rem;\">\n<svg width=\"32\" height=\"32\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"white\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path d=\"M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z\"></path></svg>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"text-teal\">合规性</h3>\n<p>临界合规监管？权衡控制力与便利性。</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>"
}
